data.title: My 700th Published Article! A Look Back at Every Movie I Have Ever Reviewed!
data.meta_description: I have kept a running count of every article I have ever written and published for a few years now. This includes movie, music, and TV reviews, along with other types of posts, like opinion and satire pieces. Since I’ve kept all my files going back to 2002, when I began writing for The Denver Post’s “Colorado Kids,” the list is a very accurate archive…
data.text:
I have kept a running count of every article I have ever written and published for a few years now.
